---
description: Server tests — run before finishing backend changes
globs: server/**/*.test.js, server/tests/**
alwaysApply: false
---

# Testing

- Run: `cd server && npm test`
- Tests live in `server/tests/`; use existing patterns (`supertest` + exported `app`)
- Fix failing tests before marking work complete
- Prefer behavior assertions (status, JSON shape) over implementation details

When adding an endpoint, add or update a test in the same change when practical.
